Megatron landed beside Triggerhappy. He looked down and scowled, lightly
kicking the Targetmaster. "Show some pride, your a Decepticon. If I
wasnt low on soldiers I would think about leaving you." He looked around
the battlefield again, then back down to Triggerhappy. "Does Blowpipe
have any energy left?"
